MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2002-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 9th May, 2002
19 Vaisakha, 1924(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 9th May,
2002 :-
Shri Manohar Joshi relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
Heavy Industries and Public Enterprises; and
i)
Shri Suresh Prabhu assumed the charge of the office of Minister of
Heavy Industries and Public Enterprises. He will continue to hold the
charge of the office of Minister of Power.
ii)
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
